summary: Geologist with high expertise in the characterization and prediction of reservoir quality (clastic, carbonate and hybrid rocks). High skilled in integrated analysis of diverse datasets (sedimentology, sedimentary petrography, diagenesis, sequence stratigraphy, structural geology, geochemistry and petrophysics). Worked for 4 years in academic projects providing petrological analysis (Siliciclastic reservoirs). Strong background in drilling operations with a demonstrated working experience in the evaluation of drilled cutting samples, installation and maintenance of different sensors and gas detectors, creation of lithological profile and well logs, drilling data monitoring and reporting and preparation of technical reports.  Skilled in surface and downhole hardware and tools necessary to perform MWD/LWD services. High skilled on reservoir characterization integrating MWD/LWD and WL Logging with thin sections (single and multi-well interpretation). Entrepreneur in the jewelry and gemstones sectors, responsible for the company's management, financial, planning and strategy, daily operations, sales, marketing and  customer service. Strong interpersonal, presentation and communication skills.
